    All Field Names in a clinicaltrials.gov Record

    all_fields.Rd

    Character vector containing all queriable field names in a clinicaltrials.gov record

    Usage

    data(all_fields)

    Format

    A character vector with the names of all 322 queriable fields

    Source

    https://clinicaltrials.gov/api/info/study_fields_list?fmt=JSON

    Examples
